                  Proof 4. becauſe the alteration of it from Evening to morning, or midnight (which thwarts the Scripture computation) would falſiſie, corrupt many Paſſages and Texts of Scripture; call into queſtion the truh of our Saviours Reſurrection on the third day; and ſomewhat alter the Scripture Chronology, which is moſt exact and punctuall;


